{"word":"G2253 - ἡμιθανής - hēmithanḗs - hay-mee-than-ace' - Half dead","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἡμιθανής</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hēmithanḗs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hay-mee-than-ace'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Half dead</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"குற்றுயிரான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"half dead"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a presumed compound of the base of <a href=\"#/G2255 - ἥμισυ - hḗmisy - hay'-mee-soo/2255\">G2255</a> and <a href=\"#/G2348 - θνήσκω - thnḗskō - thnay'-sko/2348\">G2348</a>; <i>half dead</i>, that is, <i>entirely exhausted:</i> - half dead.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}